      "framing_strong": "Important framing:",
      "framing_body": "simulators are imperfect approximations. They are useful for empathy-building and rápido checks, NOT for verifying compliance. A protanopia filtrar is NOT the same as protanopia. Real users have lived with their condition; you are seeing it for 60 seconds. Usar simulators to surface obvious problems (cor-only informação, low contrast, illegible texto), then teste with real users when stakes matter.",
